description.en: flyte scribe is a blog written by edo/flyte, telling the interwebs about his current life at Tokyo, Japan. Mainly talks about photography and the like.
description.ga_IE: Is blag é an Scríobhaí Flyte a scríobh Edo / Flyte, ag insint na n-interwebs faoina shaol reatha ag Tóiceo, an tSeapáin.Den chuid is mó cainteanna faoi grianghrafadóireacht agus a leithéidí.
